title: [New Team]Recruiting team member for OOL ( Prefer : JG SUP and ADC ) gold / plat+
body:
We are currently the newcomers that are interested in joining OOL for our first time. 
If any of you feel interested and come up any idea or question, feel free to contact "superyan" or "SBDog" at any time 
Please send one of us your preferred lane and which champs / lanes are your strongest, team allocation will be made once everyone are joined.
